snippet.title: Realms Beyond - Combat Alpha 1 Gameplay
snippet.description:
Late backer can support us here: https://realms-beyond.backerkit.com/hosted_preorders

https://www.realms-beyond.com

Ambush in the Forest

A battle taken from the alpha version of our combat system.

While traveling through woodlands on the worldmap, the player's party has been ambushed by a group of orcs and trolls 

Reminder: Particularly the user Interface, sounds, FXs and animations are still work in progress.


Music by Bastian Kieslinger.
